me1200MepMib.name: me1200MepMib

revisions.description: Added support for Loss Measurement Availability. Added option to view DM FD and IFDV bin values in me1200StatusDmFdBinsTable and me1200StatusDmIfdvBinsTable.
Fixed description of default value for me1200ConfigDmNumOfBinIFDV. Fixed spelling mistake: 'Dealy' changed to 'Delay' in OID names.
Added me1200ConfigDmNumOfBinFD, me1200ConfigDmNumOfBinIFDV and me1200ConfigDmMThreshold objects.
Added support for LM IntervalElapsed object
Added support for SLM multiple peers and capabilities update
Adding notification of frame loss raito
Adding of Link State Tracking functionality
Definition of lbToSendInfinite is added to vtss_appl_mep_capabilities_t and numerics are removed from descriptions and replaced with Capability reference
Definition of type InterfaceIndex changed from Unsigned32 to Integer32 as it is used as index in some tables
Do no use Unsigned32 for indexes
MIB has been added to support Dynamic CCM TLV in the MEP module
